== Aitsu_Util_Date :: secondsUntilEndOf(year|month|day|week) ==

Use this method to get the seconds from now to the end of the year, end of the current
month, end of the current day or the end of the current week.

Aitsu_Util_Date :: secondsUntilEndOf('week') returns the time difference in seconds
from now to next Monday 0 a.m.